"As Head Researcher, I need a confirmation page to be displayed once the user has clicked the ‘submit’ button 
so that participants know they have successfully submitted the form"
Label: Deliver Last (Low Risk/Low Value) 
MOSCOW: Should

Background:  After participants complete the questionnaire, a confirmation page should be displayed, this is to confirm that the form 
has been submitted and allows for the researcher to leave a message saying thankyou along with any other relevant information that
the participants need to know.  the researcher has asked for space for roughly two paragraphs as well as allocated space for
email address and contact information.  In this instance email and contact information will be kept as a John/Jane Doe and 
paragraphs just to contain sample data, such as Lorem ipsum.
